service-1", "cartservice-0", "frontend-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "currencyservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "frontend-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["shippingservice-1", "redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-10T07:10:44Z to 2025-06-10T07:28:44Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-10 07:10:44+00:00 to 2025-06-10 07:28:44+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-0", "frontend-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "currencyservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "frontend-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["shippingservice-1", "redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "node_memory_usage_rate", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "log_analysis_findings": "根据从日志中检索到的数据，我们可以进行如下分析：\n\n### 错误模式分析\n从日志中获取到的所有错误信息均来自 `frontend` 服务，这些日志传达出的主要问题是无法与 `shippingservice` 成功建立连接，具体表现为 \"connection refused\" 错误。这种情况通常暗示着可能存在端口配置错误或是 `shippingservice` 无法在指定端口上进行监听。\n\n#### 提取的关键词\n- **错误类型**: `ConnectionRefused`, `Unavailable`, `transport: Error while dialing`\n- **日志标签**: `shippingservice--connection refused`\n\n### 根因分析\n在全部检测到的日志中，`frontend` 服务抱怨无法连接到 `shippingservice` 的特定地址（`dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051`），而该错误是由于连接被拒绝。在这种情况下，`shippingservice` 是被调方服务，异常可能根源于该节点的端口配置错误。\n\n### JSON 输出\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"ConnectionRefused\", \"transport: Error while dialing\", \"shippingservice--connection refused\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Detected connection refused errors indicating potential port misconfiguration issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: connect: connection refused\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n根据分析结果，日志中明确指出 `shippingservice` 是异常发生的核心组件，并且给出了详细的日志证据支持初步假设，即该服务因为端口配置错误或服务不可用造成了系统故障。此分析支持原初步假设关于 `shippingservice` 的问题。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据异常指标数据分析结果，我们可以进行假设验证。以下是从 `raw_metric_result` 中提取的关键信息：\n\n### 异常指标观察\n\n1. **Shipping Service**:\n   - Pod `shippingservice-1` 的 `client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 显著增加，达到 31.66，表明服务故障。\n   - `shippingservice-1` 的 `rrt_max` 在异常期间表现出较大的变化，虽然变化率不大，但依然显著。\n\n2. **Node 及其他服务**：\n   - `aiops-k8s-08` 节点上的内存使用率有所下降，不显示故障。\n   - 其他服务的错误率虽增加但未达到 `shippingservice-1` 的程度。\n\n### 验证分析\n- **Fault Attribution**: `shippingservice-1` 的错误率在故障期间急剧上升，而 `client_error_ratio` 也显著增加，显示了服务不稳定性。\n- **服务影响**: 结合其他服务调用链上的延迟，特别是涉及 `checkoutservice` 和 `shipping service`，支持 shipping service 是根本故障来源的假设。\n\n### 结论\n\n- 故障期间的异常数据支持 `shipping service` 出现了端口配置错误或服务不可用的问题。\n- `shippingservice-1` 是主要的故障来源。\n\n### 输出结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Shipping service experienced a significant increase in error_ratio and client_error_ratio, indicating port misconfiguration or service unavailability.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio fault value 31.66; error_ratio increase during fault period\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n该数据分析结果支持初步假设，并增强了对 shipping service 作为故障根因的确认。我们可以继续下一步动作以解决或进一步研究这些问题。", "trace_analysis_findings": "### 验证分析\n\n根据获取的异常调用链数据，我们需要就 `shipping service` 是否为故障的根因进行分析。以下是从追踪数据中提取的关键信息：\n\n1. **延迟情况**\n   - `shippingservice` 在异常期间的调用平均耗时（`anomaly_avg_duration`）相比正常期间（`normal_avg_duration`）显著增加。例如，`frontend` 调用 `shippingservice` 的 `GetQuote` 操作，平均延迟从 `201.39ms` 增加到 `523.0ms`（大约是 2.6 倍），表明存在延迟问题。\n\n2. **错误状态**\n   - `checkoutservice` 调用 `shippingservice` 获取报价时，出现多个 `connection refused` 错误，明确指向 `shippingservice` 的不可用或端口配置错误问题。\n   - 错误信息显示有多个 `Unavailable` 和 `Connection refused` 错误，特别是在调用 `hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote` 时，这与初步假设一致。\n\n3. **调用链影响**\n   - `checkoutservice` 在执行 `PlaceOrder` 时依赖 `shippingservice`，但由于连接被拒绝，引发后续操作失败，显示 `shippingservice` 是故障链中较下游的关键影响因素。\n\n### 结论\n\n基于以上分析数据，`shippingservice` 确实表现出多个含有 `connection refused` 和 `Unavailable` 错误的状态，而延迟倍数及系统调用的依赖关系进一步支持了初始假设。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\", \"shippingservice->unavailable or connection refused\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"The average duration increased from 201.39ms to 523.0ms, indicating significant delays.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frequent 'connection refused' and 'Unavailable' errors indicate service unavailability or port misconfiguration.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n结论是当前假设成立，`shippingservice` 因端口错误或不可用性而成为问题根源，影响了整个系统的响应时间和可用性。这符合之前的初步假设。"}
